        <reimplements refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdateTyped_1afbee40c70e2b878b49a2794388ce8290">Apply</reimplements>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Apply the pending changes and return the uncommitted result. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This does not result in a permanent update.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>the uncommitted changes that would be committed, or an error:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>ValidationFailed: if pending changes cannot be applied</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>InvalidArgument: if pending changes are conflicting </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
