        <reimplements refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdate_1a0643491619bb8e88a60943e5546adcb6">Commit</reimplements>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Apply and commit the pending changes to the table. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Changes are committed by calling the underlying table&apos;s commit operation.</para>
<para>Once the commit is successful, the updated table will be refreshed.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>Status::OK if the commit was successful, or an error:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>ValidationFailed: if update cannot be applied to current metadata</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>CommitFailed: if update cannot be committed due to conflicts</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>CommitStateUnknown: if commit success state is unknown </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
